Class UnreliabilityFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jreliability.function.SequentialFunction
      • org.jreliability.function.UnreliabilityFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function
    public class UnreliabilityFunction
extends SequentialFunction
    The UnreliabilityFunction determines the UnreliabilityFunction F(x) of a given ReliabilityFunction R(x) as

    F(x) = 1 - R(x).
